ğŸ§  Mental model (remember this)
Edit files â†’ git add â†’ git commit â†’ git push


Nothing reaches GitHub until push.

ğŸ§¹ Optional (one-time, recommended)

Create .gitattributes in repo root:

*.py  text eol=lf
*.sql text eol=lf
*.R   text eol=lf


This avoids Windows line-ending warnings forever.

